#: ../../source/examples.md:7
msgid ""
"⚠️ **重要提示**：本框架中的所有装饰器（`@llm_function`、`@llm_chat`、`@tool`）均要求被装饰的函数使用 "
"`async def` 定义，并在调用时通过 `await`（或 `asyncio.run`）执行。"
msgstr ""
"⚠️ **Important Reminder**: All decorators in this framework "
"(`@llm_function`, `@llm_chat`, `@tool`) require the decorated function to be"
" defined using `async def` and executed using `await` (or `asyncio.run`) "
"when called."

